  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BolusCalcComponent
    Represents data about a component of the total Bolus calculation, with its insulin amount and conditions which resulted in that insulin amount being decided.
    BolusCalcCondition.BolusCalcPrompt  
    BolusCalcDecision
    Represents data about the completed Bolus calculation, with the insulin amounts via BolusCalcUnits and the conditions which resulted in those insulin amounts being decided.
    BolusCalcLastBG  
    BolusCalculator
    Contains logic for deciding an estimated bolus amount given inputs and current pump/CGM status.
    BolusCalculatorBuilder
    A builder object for filling data into BolusCalculator when response messages are received from the pump.
    BolusCalcUnits
    An object representing the units for each component of the bolus calculation.
